            "text": "Yes. Foxit handles the same core tasks — editing, signing, converting, redacting, and collaborating on PDFs — at a lower price point. Many businesses and government agencies use Foxit as their primary PDF solution, and its AI features actually surpass what Adobe offers in some areas like smart redaction.",
